This is the project of DSGE, which replicate the results of the paper: Differentiable State-Space Models and Hamiltonian Monte Carlo Estimation, David Childers, Jesus Fernandez-Villaverde, etc.

There are three pdf files and 1 code folder.
1. Proposal.pdf describe the motivation and workflow of this work.
2. Report.pdf consists of the replication results and question answering to the interview questions.
3. DSGE in a Nutshell is a notes to help student to understand DSGE model and handle the basic solution method.

The code folder has three sub folders: 
1. src: contain all of the main code.
2. tests: contain all of the test code.
3. data: contain the data we used for inference.

